scopecontent.p:
Topics covered in these pamphlets include: collective bargaining; the economic conditions and policy of the Federal Republic of Germany from the period immediately after its founding through and after the reunification in 1990; environmental policy; the
    European Union and its predecessors; guest workers; postwar politics in Germany; social security; strikes and lockouts; training and education for workers; unemployment; wages; white collar unions; women in the workforce and in the unions; working hours;
    and works councils and other forms of worker participation in management.
